    <td class="roweven" valign="top" width="2000">Critical bug FIXED: Alignment of code failed on indents with tabs. Realized that stridx() and matchend() read a tab as 1 space, instead of the correct &tabstop number of spaces. Thanks to Christian Brehm!<br><br>Renamed options to g:vhdl_indent_genportmap & g:vhdl_indent_rhsassign, to be consistent with naming convention.</td>
</tr>
